firmation as to whether the account remains with Prodigy Finance or has been assigned or transferred to any third party. If transferred, please provide the details. \\n\\n\\n\\nHoping to hear from you soon.\\nThank you for your understanding.\\n\\nRegards,\\nTolulope O. Omotayo", "date_and_timestamp": "4/5/2026 18:07", "customer / account / loan id": "customer_id_2"}, {"message_content": "Good afternoon Andisiwe.\\nI sent an email to Prodigy last Monday and i'm yet to receive a response.\\nMy request is for a payoff statement with some details requested. I am not asking for a settlement offer at this moment as responded to by your AI agent.\\nKindly have a look into the email and let me have the requested information as detailed in my email - Subject: Loan ID PDGUS271931 – Request for Payoff Statement.\\nHoping to hear from you soon.\\nHave a blessed day.\\n\\n\\nRegards,\\nTolulope O. Omotayo", "date_and_timestamp": "4/4/2026 10:09", "customer / account / loan id": "customer_id_2"}, {"message_content": "Hi Tolulope,\\n \\nFrom point 1-4, I provided a full transactional statement to confirm the relevant information.\\n \\n5. A settlement offer was provided to confirm the settlement amount which is valid till 30 March 2026.\\n \\n6. The current status is delinquent.\\n \\n7. The account is still maintained by Prodigy Finance.\\n \\nWe hope this gives you the clarity you need.\\n \\nIf you need further assistance, please let us know and we’ll be happy to help!\\n \\nKind regards,\\nThaakirah", "date_and_timestamp": "3/5/2026 17:28", "customer / account / loan id": "customer_id_2"}, {"message_content": "However, my requests are detailed in the letter sent to you.\\nThey are here listed below. The letter is also attached again.\\n \\n\\n1. The original principal amount disbursed to Boston University in December 2021. \\n\\n2. A detailed breakdown of all interest accrued to date, including any capitalized interest. \\n\\n3. A breakdown of any late fees, penalties, or additional charges applied to the account. \\n\\n4. A transaction history showing how my $6,000 payment made in December 2023 was applied (whether to principal, interest, or fees). \\n\\n5. The current total payoff amount as of the date of your response. \\n\\n6. Confirmation of the present status of the account. In that regard, I would like to know the status is current, delinquent, defaulted, charged off, or otherwise. \\n\\n7. Confirmation as to whether the account remains with Prodigy Finance or has been assigned or transferred to any third party. If transferred, please provide the details. \\n\\n\\n\\nHoping to hear from you soon.\\nThank you for your understanding.\\n\\nRegards,\\nTolulope O. Omotayo", "date_and_timestamp": "3/5/2026 15:24", "customer / account / loan id": "customer_id_2"}, {"message_content": "Good afternoon Andisiwe.\\nI sent an email to Prodigy last Monday and i'm yet to receive a response.\\nMy request is for a payoff statement with some details requested. I am not asking for a settlement offer at this moment as responded to by your AI agent.\\nKindly have a look into the email and let me have the requested information as detailed in my email - Subject: Loan ID PDGUS271931 – Request for Payoff Statement.\\nHoping to hear from you soon.\\nHave a blessed day.\\n\\n\\nRegards,\\nTolulope O. Omotayo", "date_and_timestamp": "3/4/2026 13:21", "customer / account / loan id": "customer_id_2"}], "_payment_count": 1, "_conversation_count": 7, "customer / account / loan id": "customer_id_2"}	\N		10	Customer explicitly lists 7 points of required information in emails on 2026-03-05 and 2026-04-05, stating 'my requests are detailed in the letter sent to you' and clarifying 'I am not asking for a settlement offer at this moment'.	Agent Review. The customer is disputing the debt, which is a mandatory trigger for human escalation as per the ESCALATION RULES. An agent must investigate, provide the detailed statements requested, and manage the dispute. Automated treatments are not appropriate.	10	The ESCALATION RULES state to 'always route to human when: ... Customer disputes the debt'. The customer's detailed request for financial information and a payoff statement constitutes a dispute that requires manual handling.		0	The ability to pay is calculated based on the median of successful payments in the last 3 months. As there have been no payments in this period, the calculated capacity is $0.	0	NO_ACTION	{"willingness": "VERY LOW", "combined_cmd": null, "conversation": "Customer has proactively emailed multiple times in March and April 2026 requesting a detailed breakdown of the loan (principal, interest, fees, payment application) and a payoff statement. The customer is disputing the information provided and seeking clarity on the total amount owed.", "affordability": "VERY LOW", "customer_guid": "customer_id_2", "vulnerability": false, "ability_to_pay": 0, "internal_action": "", "payment_history": "No payment activity in the last 6 months. Last successful payment: $6000.00 on Dec 8, 2023 (over 2 years ago).", "problem_evidence": "Customer explicitly lists 7 points of required information in emails on 2026-03-05 and 2026-04-05, stating 'my requests are detailed in the letter sent to you' and clarifying 'I am not asking for a settlement offer at this moment'.", "proposed_solution": "Agent Review. The customer is disputing the debt, which is a mandatory trigger for human escalation as per the ESCALATION RULES. An agent must investigate, provide the detailed statements requested, and manage the dispute. Automated treatments are not appropriate.", "solution_evidence": "The ESCALATION RULES state to 'always route to human when: ... Customer disputes the debt'. The customer's detailed request for financial information and a payoff statement constitutes a dispute that requires manual handling.", "problem_description": "", "arrears_clearance_plan": null, "reason_for_willingness": "Insufficient engagement signals to determine wi